summary:
- **Performance Rights Issuance**: 133,282 unquoted performance rights (ASX code: DNLAJ) issued to KMP Nitesh Naidoo on 07/07/2025 under an employee incentive scheme.  
- **Vesting Terms**: Vesting later of 31/12/2025 or 6 months post commencement, subject to employment and performance conditions. No dividend/voting rights; converts to 1 ordinary share per vested right.  
- **Total Securities**: Post-issue, unquoted performance rights (DNLAJ) total 5,532,693; ordinary shares (DNL) remain at 1,842,454,876.  

*No material trading or capital markets impact identified (routine employee incentive issuance).*
